Ge4:23 One day, Lamech said to his two wives, "A young man wounded me, and I killed him.
Ge4:24 Anyone who tries to get even with me will be punished ten times more than anyone who tries to get even with Cain."
Ge4:25 Adam and his wife had another son. They named him Seth, because they said, "God has given us a son to take the place of Abel, who was killed by his brother Cain."
Ge4:26 Later, Seth had a son and named him Enosh. About this time people started worshiping the Lord .
