Exo21:30 However, you may save your own life by paying whatever fine is demanded.
Exo21:31 This same law applies if the bull gores someone's son or daughter.
Exo21:32 If the bull kills a slave, you must pay the slave owner thirty pieces of silver for the loss of the slave, and the bull must be killed by stoning.
