Exo29:39 one in the morning and one in the evening.
Exo29:40 With each lamb offer two pounds of your finest flour mixed with a quart of pure olive oil, and also pour out a quart of wine as an offering. The smell of this sacrifice on the fires of the altar will be pleasing to me.
Exo29:41 ...
