Num3:17 Levi's three sons, Gershon, Kohath, and Merari, had become the heads of their own clans.
Num3:18 Gershon's sons were Libni and Shimei.
Num3:19 Kohath's sons were Amram, Izhar, Hebron, and Uzziel.
Num3:20 And Merari's sons were Mahli and Mushi. These were the sons and grandsons of Levi, and they had become the leaders of the Levite clans.
