Deu16:4 ...
Deu16:5 Don't offer the Passover sacrifice in just any town where you happen to live.
Deu16:6 It must be offered at the place where the Lord chooses to be worshiped. Kill the sacrifice at sunset, the time of day when you left Egypt.
