2Sm22:27 With all who are sincere you are sincere, but you treat the unfaithful as their deeds deserve.
2Sm22:28 You rescue the humble, but you look for ways to put down the proud.
2Sm22:29 Our Lord and God, you are my lamp. You turn darkness to light.
