1Chr27:2 In the first month, Jashobeam the son of Zabdiel,
1Chr27:3 a descendant of Perez;
1Chr27:4 in the second month, Dodai the Ahohite, whose assistant was Mikloth;
1Chr27:5 in the third month, Benaiah the son of Jehoiada the priest,
1Chr27:6 who was the leader of the Thirty Warriors, and whose son Ammizabad was also an army commander;
1Chr27:7 in the fourth month, Asahel the brother of Joab, whose son Zebadiah took over command after him;
1Chr27:8 in the fifth month, Shamhuth from the Izrah clan;
1Chr27:9 in the sixth month, Ira the son of Ikkesh from Tekoa;
1Chr27:10 in the seventh month, Helez from Pelon in the territory of Ephraim;
1Chr27:11 in the eighth month, Sibbecai from Hushah of the Zerah clan;
1Chr27:12 in the ninth month, Abiezer from Anathoth in the territory of Benjamin;
1Chr27:13 in the tenth month, Maharai from Netophah of the Zerah clan;
1Chr27:14 in the eleventh month, Benaiah from Pirathon in the territory of Ephraim;
1Chr27:15 in the twelfth month, Heldai from Netophah, who was a descendant of Othniel.
