Psa12:4 They say to themselves, "We are great speakers. No one else has a chance."
Psa12:5 But you, Lord , tell them, "I will do something! The poor are mistreated and helpless people moan. I'll rescue all who suffer."
Psa12:6 Our Lord , you are true to your promises, and your word is like silver heated seven times in a fiery furnace.
