Psa14:4 Won't you evil people learn? You refuse to pray, and you gobble down the Lord 's people.
Psa14:5 But you will be frightened, because God is on the side of every good person.
Psa14:6 You may spoil the plans of the poor, but the Lord protects them.
Psa14:7 I long for someone from Zion to come and save Israel! Our Lord , when you bless your people again, Jacob's family will be glad, and Israel will celebrate.
Psa15:1 Who may stay in God's temple or live on the holy mountain of the Lord ?
Psa15:2 Only those who obey God and do as they should. They speak the truth
