Psa28:3 Don't drag me away, Lord , with those cruel people, who speak kind words, while planning trouble.
Psa28:4 Treat them as they deserve! Punish them for their sins.
Psa28:5 They don't pay any attention to your wonderful deeds. Now you will destroy them and leave them in ruin.
