Psa33:5 He loves justice and fairness, and he is kind to everyone everywhere on earth.
Psa33:6 The Lord made the heavens and everything in them by his word.
Psa33:7 He scooped up the ocean and stored the water.
Psa33:8 Everyone in this world should worship and honor the Lord !
Psa33:9 As soon as he spoke the world was created; at his command, the earth was formed.
Psa33:10 The Lord destroys the plans and spoils the schemes of the nations.
Psa33:11 But what the Lord has planned will stand forever. His thoughts never change.
Psa33:12 The Lord blesses each nation that worships only him. He blesses his chosen ones.
Psa33:13 The Lord looks at the world
Psa33:14 from his throne in heaven, and he watches us all.
Psa33:15 The Lord gave us each a mind, and nothing we do can be hidden from him.
