Psa39:3 I felt a fire burning inside, and the more I thought, the more it burned, until at last I said:
Psa39:4 "Please, Lord , show me my future. Will I soon be gone?
Psa39:5 You made my life short, so brief that the time means nothing to you. "Human life is but a breath,
