Psa39:7 "What am I waiting for? I depend on you, Lord!
Psa39:8 Save me from my sins. Don't let fools sneer at me.
Psa39:9 You treated me like this, and I kept silent, not saying a word.
Psa39:10 "Won't you stop punishing me? You have worn me down.
Psa39:11 You punish us severely because of our sins. Like a moth, you destroy what we treasure most. We are as frail as a breath.
Psa39:12 "Listen, Lord , to my prayer! My eyes are flooded with tears, as I pray to you. I am merely a stranger visiting in your home as my ancestors did.
