Psa40:1 I patiently waited, Lord , for you to hear my prayer. You listened
Psa40:2 and pulled me from a lonely pit full of mud and mire. You let me stand on a rock with my feet firm,
Psa40:3 and you gave me a new song, a song of praise to you. Many will see this, and they will honor and trust you, the Lord God.
Psa40:4 You bless all of those who trust you, Lord , and refuse to worship idols or follow false gods.
