Psa40:14 Disappoint and confuse all who want me dead; turn away and disgrace all who want to hurt me.
Psa40:15 Embarrass and shame all of those who say, "Just look at you now!"
Psa40:16 Our Lord , let your worshipers rejoice and be glad. They love you for saving them, so let them always say, "The Lord is wonderful!"
Psa40:17 I am poor and needy, but, Lord God, you care about me, and you come to my rescue. Please hurry and help.
Psa41:1 You, Lord God, bless everyone who cares for the poor, and you rescue those people in times of trouble.
