Psa44:23 Wake up! Do something, Lord! Why are you sleeping? Don't desert us forever.
Psa44:24 Why do you keep looking away? Don't forget our sufferings and all of our troubles.
Psa44:25 We are flat on the ground, holding on to the dust.
Psa44:26 Do something! Help us! Show how kind you are and come to our rescue.
Psa45:1 My thoughts are filled with beautiful words for the king, and I will use my voice as a writer would use pen and ink.
