Dan2:6 However, if you do tell me both the dream and its meaning, you will be greatly rewarded and highly honored. Now tell me the dream and explain what it means."
Dan2:7 "Your Majesty," they said, "if you will only tell us your dream, we will interpret it for you."
Dan2:8 The king replied, "You're just stalling for time,
