Dan2:18 Then he said, "Pray that the God who rules from heaven will be merciful and explain this mystery, so that we and the others won't be put to death."
Dan2:19 In a vision one night, Daniel was shown the dream and its meaning. Then he praised the God who rules from heaven:
Dan2:20 "Our God, your name will be praised forever and forever. You are all-powerful, and you know everything.
