Mat13:45 The kingdom of heaven is like what happens when a shop owner is looking for fine pearls.
Mat13:46 After finding a very valuable one, the owner goes and sells everything in order to buy that pearl.
Mat13:47 The kingdom of heaven is like what happens when a net is thrown into a lake and catches all kinds of fish.
