Mark3:11 And whenever any evil spirits saw Jesus, they would fall to the ground and shout, "You are the Son of God!"
Mark3:12 But Jesus warned the spirits not to tell who he was.
Mark3:13 Jesus decided to ask some of his disciples to go up on a mountain with him, and they went.
