Mark5:14 The men taking care of the pigs ran to the town and the farms to spread the news. Then the people came out to see what had happened.
Mark5:15 When they came to Jesus, they saw the man who had once been full of demons. He was sitting there with his clothes on and in his right mind, and they were terrified.
