John15:23 Everyone who hates me also hates my Father.
John15:24 I have done things that no one else has ever done. If they had not seen me do these things, they would not be guilty. But they did see me do these things, and they still hate me and my Father too.
John15:25 That is why the Scriptures are true when they say, "People hated me for no reason."
John15:26 I will send you the Spirit who comes from the Father and shows what is true. The Spirit will help you and will tell you about me.
